data.description: SAVE up to $80 over new Quadrant home of similar size - HOME WARRANTY PROVIDED and NO HOMEOWNERS DUES. EASY 5-BEDROOM CONVERSION! Walk to the public park and elementary school. Generous oversized master and walk-in closets in each and every bedroom. Spacious kitchen boasts a large island/eating bar and abundant counters, lower cabinets with custom roll out drawers and a large walk-in pantry. Kitchen window overlooks a fenced, manicured backyard which features a garden space and apple tree...
data.whatILove: Lots of space in this 3040 sf home. Every room is large. Could easily be 5 bedroom home by enclosing open space on 2nd floor. Pergo floors downstairs, walk-in closets in all bedrooms, large walk-in pantry. (Master bdrm - 16x18) (2 bedrooms- 14x14) (1 bedroom - 10x19). (Family room - 16x17) (Open area upstairs - could be 5th bedroom - 11x14) (Living room - 13x20) ...... .(Buyer to verify measurements to own satisfaction)
